name: TLPS
description: TLPS, June 3 - July 9, 2021. Lydian Stater is excited to present TLPS, an exhibition featuring first-ever NFT works from ten artists: Jeffrey Michael Austin, Marcos Castro, Matthew Cronin, Yi Hsuan Lai, Marta Rodriguez Maleck, Cedric Tai, Anika Todd, Catalina Tuca, Victor Yañez-Lazcano, and Alisa Yang.
